---
import Heading from "./typography/Heading.astro"
import Bodytext from "./typography/Bodytext.astro"
---
<section aria-label="FAQ" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <Heading level={2} class="text-primary-50">Frequently Asked Questions</Heading>
<div class="space-y-4">
    <!-- FAQ Item -->
    <details class="p-4">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-primary-700 font-semibold text-primary-50">
            Is there camping available?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-primary-50">&#9660;</span> <!-- â–¼ vises her -->
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 text-primary-50">
            Yes, camping is available for all ticket holders. Please check our website for details on camping areas and facilities.
        </p>
        <hr class="my-6 border-t border-primary-100" />
    </details>

    <details class="group border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-primary-700 font-semibold text-primary-50">
            What food and drink options are available?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-primary-50">&#9660;</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 text-primary-50">
            We offer a variety of food trucks and stalls, including vegetarian and vegan options, as well as several bars serving drinks.
        </p>
    </details>

    <details class="group border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-primary-700 font-semibold text-primary-50">
            Can I volunteer at the festival?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-primary-50">&#9660;</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 text-primary-50">
            Absolutely! We welcome volunteers. Please visit our volunteer page to learn more and sign up.
        </p>
    </details>
</div>
</section>

</section>